'''吉吉加'''（'''Jijiga'''，[[索馬里語|索馬里語]]︰''Jigjiga''）是[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]東部的城市，也是[[索馬里州|索馬里州]]的首府，海拔1,609米，座標{{Coord|9|21|N|42|48|E}}，位於[[哈勒爾|哈勒爾]]以東80公里（50英哩）。根據[[埃塞俄比亞中央統計局|埃塞俄比亞中央統計局]]2005年的人口普查資料，吉吉加總人口約98,076人，其中男性50,355人，女性47,721人<ref>[http://www.csa.gov.et/text_files/2005_national_statistics.htm CSA 2005 National Statistics] {{Wayback|url=http://www.csa.gov.et/text_files/2005_national_statistics.htm |date=20070813054932 }}, Table B.4</ref>，[[索馬里人|索馬里人]]佔61.58%<ref>[http://www.csa.gov.et/surveys/Population%20and%20Housing%20Census%201994/survey0/data/docs%5Creport%5CStatistical_Report%5Ck05%5Ck05.pdf ''1994 Population and Housing Census of Ethiopia: Results for Somali Region, Vol. 1''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.csa.gov.et/surveys/Population%20and%20Housing%20Census%201994/survey0/data/docs%5Creport%5CStatistical_Report%5Ck05%5Ck05.pdf |date=20081119230720 }} Tables 2.4, 2.14 (accessed 10 January 2009). The results of the 1994 census in the Somali Region were not satisfactory, so the census was repeated in 1997.</ref>。雖然這地區植物不多，但曾經是[[非洲野犬|非洲野犬]]的棲息地，後來因人口膨脹而遷居別地。<ref>C. Michael Hogan. 2009. [http://globaltwitcher.auderis.se/artspec_information.asp?thingid=35993 ''Painted Hunting Dog: Lycaon pictus'', GlobalTwitcher.com, ed. N. Stromberg] {{Wayback|url=http://globaltwitcher.auderis.se/artspec_information.asp?thingid=35993 |date=20101209234758 }}</ref>

